headline: Goldman Sachs upgrades Fiserv on its growth catalysts amid fintech weakness
summary: Investing.com -- Goldman Sachs upgraded Fiserv Inc (NYSE:FI) to "Buy," citing product-driven revenue acceleration and an attractive valuation, while also upgrading Jack Henry & Associates (NASDAQ:JKHY) to "Neutral" as fintech stocks struggle amid a weaker macro backdrop.
